*** Context ***
+ A project is created without Execution Environment
+ The outline view is open

*** Actions ***
- Open the main.lua file
- Declare a local variable outside of the main function declaration
- Introduce an error in the code
- Declare a new local variable after the error
- Declare a new function after the error
- Declare a new local variable before the error
# Check 1
- Remove the error part of the code
# Check 2

*** Assertions ***
# Check 1 : Only functions and variables declared before the error writting appear in the outline view
# Check 2 : All declared functions and variables appear in the outline view
